         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">South-Yarra, ¶ 12 May 1893 ¶ T. R. Wilson Esqr ¶ Under Secretary. ¶  ¶ In reply to your memorandum, received this afternoon by telephone, I beg respectfully to state, that  ¶ the Staff ¶   ¶ in the Go...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">93.05.12</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">W93/3729, unit 818, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Check unit no,</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>South-Yarra,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">12 May 1893</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">T. R. Wilson Esqr</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Under Secretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reply to your memorandum, received this afternoon by telephone, I beg respectfully to state, that <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">the Staff</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">in the Gov. Botanists</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Establishment</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">is not in excess of requirements</hi>
               </seg>. The demands for information on my branch of the service are overwhelming, and the estimates for the new finance-year are in proportion to other Institutions very limited, while the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">correspondence is very extensive</hi>
               </seg>, and the maintenance and utilisation of the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">vast Herbarium</hi>
               </seg> requires such great care. I would therefore solicit, that my <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">small</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">staff</hi>
               </seg> may remain through the kindness of the honorable the Chief Secretary</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be, Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gov. Botanist</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I may add, that I have <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">two juniors</hi>
               </seg> employed since many months on my own expense in the establishment and must continue them also hereafter<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">On 17 May 1893 Wilson minuted: 'Seen by C. S. — no change'.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
